      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VICTA HOWARD (8) is rarely out of the finish, recording 13 places from 24 starts. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when third (31.33) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from six starts. Key chance in this line up. JETSON (2) is a consistent type who is having his first try here. Comes here a winner after using the inside draw to advantage last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths at Murray Bridge over 455m (25.83). Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. WILMA'S OUR GIRL (1) placed last time (34.51) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten one length. Looks well placed here and among the chances. HIJINKERY (4) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
